## 🕌 Bonus Project: CLI Prayer Time

Fetches live Islamic prayer times for any city and highlights the next upcoming prayer in the terminal.

```bash
cd CLI-prayer-time
node prayer-time.js
```

**Concepts used:** `readline`, `async/await`, `fetch`, `Date` manipulation, ANSI terminal colors.

